<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='287506' id='t-287506'>by good guys, or by bad guys.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 5:00
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='289980' id='t-289980'>And so for that reason,
I think that it's better</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='292523' id='t-292523'>to build networks
to be as secure as possible.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='296271' id='t-296271'>Yes, this means that in the future,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='298704' id='t-298704'>encryption is going to make
