 5:45
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='334737' id='t-334737'>And so, my message to you is this:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='338110' id='t-338110'>We need to use these tools.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='340239' id='t-340239'>We need to secure our telephone calls.</span>
